[base]
# Metrics Module
histogram.rs: HDR histogram (p50/p95/p99/p999). recall.rs: recall@K.
export.rs: CSV + JSON. distance.rs: SIMD distance (cosine, L2, IP).
SimSIMD with runtime CPU detection for dispatch.

[debug]
Histogram overflow: increase max_value if latencies >10s.
SIMD dispatch: SIMSIMD_LOG=1 to verify codepath.
Recall O(N*K): use --sample-queries for large datasets.

[command:debug:check-simd-dispatch]
Verify SIMD: cargo test test_simd_dispatch -- --nocapture, then cargo bench -- distance.

[skill:debug:latency-analysis]
# Latency Analysis
Check p99/p50 ratio. If >10x: tail latency issue.
Bimodal distribution = pool contention. Compare across ef_runtime values.

[inherit]
parent: mcp
